      "source": [
        "# 双均线策略\n",
        "\n",
        "把上面的直觉写成 **可执行的规则**（伪代码）：\n",
        "\n",
        "```text\n",
        "如果 MA5 > MA20:\n",
        "    持有 / 买入\n",
        "否则:\n",
        "    空仓 / 卖出\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "这就是著名的 **双均线策略（Moving Average Crossover）** 的最简版本。\n",
        "\n",
        "在 pandas 里，`signal = 1` 表示持仓，`0` 表示空仓：\n"
      ],
      "id": "ec72b841"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "# ========== 第一个策略：MA5>MA20 则持仓 ==========\n",
        "df['signal'] = (df['MA5'] > df['MA20']).astype(int)  # 满足条件=1，否则=0\n",
        "\n",
        "df['trade'] = 0                              # 默认无交易\n",
        "df.loc[df['cross'] > 0, 'trade'] = 1         # 金叉日标记买入\n",
        "df.loc[df['cross'] < 0, 'trade'] = -1        # 死叉日标记卖出\n",
        "\n",
        "hold_days = df['signal'].sum()             # signal=1 的天数\n",
        "print(f'Rule: MA5 > MA20 then hold (signal=1)')  # 格式化打印\n",
        "print(f'Within sample period, about {hold_days} trading days are in holding state (total {len(df)} days)')  # 打印统计结果\n",
        "print(f'Total { (df[\"trade\"] != 0).sum() } rebalancing signals generated (buy + sell)')  # 格式化打印\n",
        "\n",
        "display(df[df['trade'] != 0][['Close', 'MA5', 'MA20', 'signal', 'trade']].tail(6))  # 在 Notebook 中美观显示表格"
      ],
      "id": "f210f3a4",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
